*mutt-1.3.28-r1 (25 Apr 2002)

  25 Apr 2002; Ryan Phillips <rphillips@gentoo.org> mutt-1.3.28-r1.ebuild :

  Mutt couldn't fcntl() the ~/Mail directory on a NFS volume.  Changed
  ebuild to enable flock() support per bug #2005.

